{
  "stem": "11174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The thickness of the wall-- of the walls must've been at least a yard with these large windows.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This, the Germans did not destroy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The beis medrash, they destroyed before they left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This they did not destroy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was left over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then the Polish people made a movie out of it, movie house out of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there's a very interesting and tragic story with, with that episode.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had a movie in the early '50s, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I read it in the Polish paper here, somebody pointed out to me and showed it to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They showed a children's movie and there were about 350 children or more, I don't remember exact, or more.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Closer to 400 children, about 30 adults that came with the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all of a sudden a fire broke out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They all got burned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This construction, it was all brick and all stones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Somehow everything got burned to the-- to the ground with the few hundred children and, and about 30 adults.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was after the war already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now generally, the Jewish population was, I would say, let's divide it in about four categories as far as the economy goes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "At least a quarter of the population was very poor, quite poor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, now when I start thinking, you know, going back to the days and the night that I wouldn't think about it, especially going to sleep, not being able to sleep, and maybe this is the reason sometime for not being able to sleep.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There is still quite a number of people until this day, although it was-- I was 21 years old and my father was the rabbi and I knew everybody through and through.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
